      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who values both performance and presence. Meticulously maintained and exhibiting the characteristics of careful ownership, it offers a refined driving experience underscored by robust mechanical integrity. Each system has been thoroughly evaluated to ensure it meets our dealership's rigorous standards for safety and reliability. This represents an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that balances sophisticated styling with enduring value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
