      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 1997 Toyota Supra Turbo featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six power plant with factory sequential twin-turbochargers. This unit is mated to a Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery and high torque capacity. The chassis retains its structural integrity with a stock double-wishbone suspension geometry and four-piston front calipers. This example is mechanically sound with a recent valve cover gasket replacement and a verified cooling system pressure test. While the finish shows light road wear, the drivetrain remains robust, offering a high-performance baseline for the purist collector.",
      "price": 33500.0,
